ActTerritorial Lands Act
Financial Administration Act
SubjectNunavut Mining Regulations
PrecisNUNAVUT MINING REGULATIONS in order to create separate mining regulations for each territory. The Northwest Territories and Nunavut Mining Regulations will be replaced by two sets of federal regulations, each applying to a different territory: the “Northwest Territories Mining Regulations” and the “Nunavut Mining Regulations.” The splitting will not generate additional regulations but rather create the administrative separation between the mining jurisdictions.
